soinnm

Class SOINNM

  • java.lang.Object
    • soinnm.SOINNM

  • public class SOINNM
extends java.lang.Object
    The M-SOINN algorithm. Allows to input a new data pattern (optionally with text label assigned to it). Processes the input and updates the topology accordingly. Manages unique ids for nodes, edges and clusters. Provides methods for getting and setting the various parameters of the algorithm.
    Author:
    Matthias Keysermann
